<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13076675/generic-page.jpg" alt="Win a holiday for 2 to Lake Garda" data-udi="umb://media/1443a3005cc34da788574ad77287256b" /></p>
<p>Italy's largest lake continues to be a favourite with visitors drawn by its distinctly Mediterranean feel with olive and lemon groves, palms and oleanders. Along the lakeside there are many lovely towns and villages, all of which have attractive old squares and bustling streets with shops and cafés. There's plenty to do for culture lovers too with both Verona and Venice within easy reach. And why not explore the lake by boat or visit the local vineyards?</p>
<h2>The prize</h2>
<p>We're giving away a seven-night holiday to <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda</a> in <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy</a>, staying at the Grand Hotel Gardone. For your chance to win, all you have to do is complete the entry form below - good luck!</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/e192695875d84995829c6abd70030892" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e192695875d84995829c6abd70030892}" title="Grand Hotel Gardone"><span class="geolocation-title"><strong>Grand Hotel Gardone, Lake Garda</strong></span></a></p>
<div class="g6">
<p><img src="/media/13073318/grand-hotel-gardone-riviera-panorama.jpg" alt="Grand Hotel Gardone exterior" data-udi="umb://media/677fab084fcc4ac1aa45ea15e8893fce" /></p>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<p><img src="/media/13073234/grand-hotel-gardone-riviera-loungers.jpg" alt="Grand Hotel Gardone exterior with sun loungers" data-udi="umb://media/28b5887712a6457fa021eecd7ae53c37" /></p>
</div>
<p>This jewel of belle époque architecture offers a traditional, elegant atmosphere and fine cuisine with personalised and attentive service in true grand Italian style. Situated on the shores of the lake with a private promenade and panoramic terrace to enjoy the stunning views. Facilities include outdoor heated swimming pool, á la carte terrace restaurant by the pool, gardens, whirlpool and small wellness area. </p>
<p><strong>Prize includes:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>7-nights Half Board accommodation at the 4* Grand Hotel Gardone</li>
<li>Return flights to Verona from London Gatwick or Manchester</li>
<li>Return transfers from Verona airport to the hotel</li>
<li>Knowledgeable Inghams service in resort</li>
<li>Holiday to be taken between 1st July &amp; 31st August 2020</li>
</ul>
<p>To be in with a chance of winning, please complete the form below.</p>
<p><strong>This competition closes on the 9th September 2019.</strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
