<li>The winner will have 2 weeks in which to accept the prize. If we do not hear from the winner in this time we will choose another winner from the competition entrants.</li>
<li>Once the prize winner is agreed all competition entrants will be notified whether they have won or not.</li>
<li>The winner will win a 7 night holiday for two to the 4 star Hotel, Grand Hotel Gardone in Lake Garda on a half board basis with Inghams.</li>
<li>The winner may take the holiday on any date between 1st July 2020 and 31st August 2020, departing Wednesday or Saturday when using Inghams Charter flights. Dates are subject to availability. </li>
