<li>The prize includes ‘Economy Class’ charter flights. Subject to availability, the winner will be able to choose to depart from any of the following UK airports: London Gatwick to Verona, and Manchester to Verona. Flights will include per person one piece of check-in luggage (luggage allowance vary from 15kg-23kg depending on carrier - exact details will be on your e-ticket). Flights are non-refundable.</li>
